OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773238282
OL,3,CBattery plant could be 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cfor valley's water supply, opponents
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FCampaigners fighting plans to build a
OL,8,Flithium storage facility on farmland
OL,9,Fin east Devon have told ITV News it
OL,10,Fcould be "catastrophic" for the
OL,11,Fvalley's water supply.
OL,13,FLast year, East Devon District Council
OL,14,Frejected plans to build a battery
OL,15,Fenergy storage system (BESS) south of
OL,16,FHazelhurst Raymonds Hill in Axminster.
OL,18,FHowever, the developer Clearstone
OL,19,Fappealed against the council's refusal
OL,20,Fof the scheme, and a public inquiry
OL,21,Freviewing the decision is now underway.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
