FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773238282
OL,3,CBattery plant could be 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cfor valley's water supply, opponents
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe plans would see a large bank of
OL,8,Fbatteries set on concrete platforms in
OL,9,Fthe field.
OL,11,FMembers of the Hawkchurch and Monkton
OL,12,FWyld Action Group (HMWAG) said they
OL,13,Fare concerned that if a fire were to
OL,14,Fbreak out on the site, the underground
OL,15,Fwater supply below could be polluted.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773238282
OL,3,CBattery plant could be 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cfor valley's water supply, opponents
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FResident Ali Watson said: "Everyone's
OL,8,Fentirely dependent on the water and if
OL,9,Fthat were to become contaminated, in
OL,10,Fany way, either through the
OL,11,Fdevelopment itself or through an
OL,12,Faccident at the site, it would be
OL,13,Fcatastrophic. It would end farming in
OL,14,Fthe valley forever."
OL,16,FKaren Goaman added that the site would
OL,17,Fbe a "blight" on the local landscape
OL,18,Fand could have a negative impact on
OL,19,Fwildlife.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773238282
OL,3,CBattery plant could be 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cfor valley's water supply, opponents
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"This is a very rural area. It's very,
OL,8,Fvery tranquil," she said.
OL,10,F"These batteries have continuous noise
OL,11,Ffrom the coolers, because the coolers
OL,12,Fare required to stop the cells of the
OL,13,Fbattery from catching fire... The
OL,14,Fimpact on wildlife would be
OL,15,Funbelievable."
OL,17,FThe developer, Clearstone Energy, has
OL,18,Fargued that there is a need for such
OL,19,Fsites to meet national energy targets
OL,20,Fand that the risk of fire is low.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773238282
OL,3,CBattery plant could be 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cfor valley's water supply, opponents
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FIn a statement, it said: "The proposal
OL,8,Fhas been designed to the highest
OL,9,Fsafety standards, and comprehensive
OL,10,Frisk assessments have been undertaken
OL,11,Fto demonstrate that environmental
OL,12,Frisks are adequately managed.
OL,14,F"Our goal is to create a low-emissions
OL,15,Fenergy secure future for Devon and the
OL,16,FUK."
OL,18,FNevertheless, the campaigners, backed
OL,19,Fby Devon CPRE, have told ITV News they
OL,20,Fwill continue to resist the appeal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
