OL,3,CBattery plant could be 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cfor valley's water supply, opponents
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe inquiry is likely to continue into
OL,8,Fnext week.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
